      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SOMELOVEFROMABOVE (4) was far too good at this track and distance last start, leading and kicking away to score by 1.8L. Suspect similar tactics will be adopted here and he only rises 1kg for the win. The form out of that has been solid and he looks set to bring up back-to-back wins. HAPPY PARK (8) was strong from the front when fresh, beaten 1.5L after sitting on the speed throughout. He'll be up front again today from the good draw and Teetan remains in the saddle. The form has already been franked and he can make an impression once more. VICTOR THE RAPID (1) won well two back before finishing strongly here again most recently, ending up 2L off the winner. He draws well again today and he's sure to be finishing off strongly from back in the pack. RIDING HIGH (10) has the early speed to roll across from out wide and with no weight on his back, he may be hard to run down.",
